EncounterIntro: A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
PlayerAction: Jack lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
RewardFeedback: Jack’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
PunishFeedback: Jack’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is injured.

EncounterIntro: In the next room, the adventurers encounter a massive stone door with intricate runes. The inscription reads, Solve the riddle to reveal what is behind." "
PlayerAction: Spencer relies on his wit to decipher the riddle.
RewardFeedback: Spencer correctly deciphers the riddle, causing the stone door to open smoothly. He finds a small room filled with treasure.
PunishFeedback: Spencer misinterprets the riddle, instead triggering a magical flash. He takes damage.

EncounterIntro: The floor is covered in a thick layer of mist. A booming voice announces, Use your wit to navigate the mist or the mist might bite.""
PlayerAction: Jack decides to use his intuition to find a way through the mist.
RewardFeedback: Jack cleverly observes the patterns in the mist, using his intelligence to discern a safe path and reach the other side unharmed.
PunishFeedback: Jack's vision is blocked by the mist, causing his to trip,  triggering a hidden trap. He suffers an injury.

EncounterIntro: A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
PlayerAction: Spencer tries to climb on the salamander’s back. He wrestles it into a choke hold.
RewardFeedback: Spencer chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. He is unharmed in the encounter.
PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Spencer’s arm. He takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

EncounterIntro: The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
PlayerAction: Spencer attempts to rely on his intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
RewardFeedback: Spencer correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. He is showered by applause from the crowd.
PunishFeedback: Spencer repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. He loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

EncounterIntro: An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
PlayerAction: Jack leaps at the ogre. He attempts to land a killing blow.
RewardFeedback: Jack stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. He is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
PunishFeedback: Jack stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. He is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

EncounterIntro: The floor of the next room is covered with small spikes.
PlayerAction: Spencer tries to use their strength to push a nearby boulder. He pushes in the direction of the spikes.
RewardFeedback: Spencer successfully pushes the boulder carving a path along the spikes. He makes it across safely.
PunishFeedback: Spencer fails to push the boulder and slips in the process. He suffer damage but is able to make it across.

EncounterIntro: Inside the next chamber is puzzle box that requires a sequence of clever moves to open.
PlayerAction: Jack tries to rely on his intelligence to open the box.
RewardFeedback: Jack was able to successfully open the box finding a valuable gemstone. He adds the gemstone to her pack.
PunishFeedback: After too many failed attempts, the box explodes in Jack’s hand. He suffers damage.

EncounterIntro: A wizard shoots an ice blast towards the players.
PlayerAction: Spencer holds up a shield and tries to overpower the blast. He then attacks the wizard.
RewardFeedback: Spencer holds steady with the shield. He stabs the wizard.
PunishFeedback: Spencer’s shield gets blown away from the blast. He stabs the wizard but is damaged from the blast.

EncounterIntro: A ditch of dense noxious gas separates the entrance and exit of this chamber. On the entrance wall is a series of crystals flashing rythmically.
PlayerAction: Jack attempts to use his wit to solve the mystery of the crystals.
RewardFeedback: Jack deciphers that the crystals required a specific sequence of touches. He inputs the sequence and waits for the gas to dissipate before proceeding.
PunishFeedback: Jack is unable to decipher the mystery of the flashing crystals. He runs across and suffers damage before pulling a lever dissipating the gas.

EncounterIntro: The duo enter a room with scalding steam vents. A rusted wheel controlling the steam flow is fixed to the wall.
PlayerAction: Jack relies on their strength to try and turn the wheel. He tries with all their might.
RewardFeedback: Jack successfully turns the valve shutting off the steam. He creates safe passage to the next chamber.
PunishFeedback: Jack is unable to turn the wheel. He is forced to dash across the hot steam and takes damage in the process.

EncounterIntro: A zombie emerges from the corner and swings its club.
PlayerAction: Spencer reflexively tried to grab the club. his attempts to overpower the swing.
RewardFeedback: Spencer successfully stops the blow. He decapitates the zombie in retaliation.
PunishFeedback: Spencer is unable to stop the attack before and suffers damage. He was able to decapitate the zombie in retaliation.

EncounterIntro: A vast pit connects the entrance and exit to the chamber.
PlayerAction: Spencer tries to leverage his cleverness to devise a way to cross.
RewardFeedback: Spencer’s throws dirt over the gap. He reveals an invisible bridge and makes it across safely.
PunishFeedback: Spencer’s unsuccessfully tries to think of a plan. He jumps across but drops some valuables from his pack.

EncounterIntro: A blind serpent patrols the next room.
PlayerAction: Jack tries to rely on his cleverness to silently outmanuever the serpent.
RewardFeedback: Jack throws a pebble to distract the serpent. He successfully distract it long enough and makes it through.
PunishFeedback: Jack tries to sneak across but slips. He makes it passed but the serpent bites their pack causing some valuables to spill.

EncounterIntro: A bridge across a chasm is lifted to be usable by a series of pulleys attached to a chain.
PlayerAction: Spencer tries to muster his strength to pull the platform up.
RewardFeedback: Spencer successfully pulls the bridge up. He latches it to a nearby pillar.
PunishFeedback: Spencer only partically pulls up the lift but not enough to be useable. He is forced to jump across dropping some valuables from their pack in the process.

EncounterIntro: A magical mirror is sits in the middle of the room. It hypnotizes the adventuerers by reflecting their deepest fears
PlayerAction: Jack relies on his mental aptitude to overcome the psychic attack.
RewardFeedback: Jack successfully breaks the hypnosis. He shatters the mirror dispelling the effect.
PunishFeedback: Jack eventually overcomes the mental anguish and is able to break the mirror. He suffers damage due to the mirror's effects.

EncounterIntro: A contending gladiator stands in front of the duo.
PlayerAction: Jack charges the gladiator and swings with all his strength.
RewardFeedback: Jack breaks through the gladiator’s attempt to block the attack. He defeats them in a single strike.
PunishFeedback: Jack bashes the gladiator defeating them but suffers a counterattack in the process. He suffers damage.

EncounterIntro: Upon entering chamber begins to fill with water. A puzzle consisting of complex symbols is next to a release valve.
PlayerAction: Spencer relies on his intellect to try to solve the puzzle.
RewardFeedback: Spencer succeeds in solving the puzzle with plenty of time. He escapes without issue.
PunishFeedback: Spencer fails numerous times before succeeding. He must drop some valuables to reach the exit before suffocating.
